Class LazyExtendedEmbedding_flat<NodeType,EdgeType>

java.lang.Object
  de.parsemis.algorithms.gSpan.LazyExtendedEmbedding_flat<NodeType,EdgeType>
Type Parameters:

EdgeType - the type of the edge labels (will be hashed and checked with .equals(..))
All Implemented Interfaces:
GSpanHPEmbedding<NodeType,EdgeType>, HPEmbedding<NodeType,EdgeType>, HPExtendedEmbedding<NodeType,EdgeType>, Frequented, Generic<NodeType,EdgeType>, java.io.Serializable
public class LazyExtendedEmbedding_flat<NodeType,EdgeType>
extends java.lang.Object
implements GSpanHPEmbedding<NodeType,EdgeType>

Implements the HPEmbedding interface for the GSpan algorithm.

It generates the embedding just if it is necessary.

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
